/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884190/extras/e97e1c1fc10cc4e671afb43787b59074.poster.avif?t=1771020988\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884190/extras/e97e1c1fc10cc4e671afb43787b59074.webm?t=1771020988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2884190/extras/e97e1c1fc10cc4e671afb43787b59074.mp4?t=1771020988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The depth of simulation and the thrill of martial arts, all in one! Build your own school, compete with rivals, and lead your fighters to the top. Join this unique adventure now and prove your mastery!</p>",
